body_html: @cy89 Hi, I resolved the error, here's what was happening: the Tensorflow for poets - 2 tutorial has all steps to get flowers_data running. But if you don't set correct version of Tensorflow to 1.5.0 in the android studio the demo keeps on stopping. The only way to get the flowers_data running is to set dependencies in the build.gradle folder to tensorflow 1.5.0, by default it is set to tensorflow 1.2.0 (you must change the default version to the version you are using).
